title: COWARDS ON YOUTUBE: Why I Hate Vegans.
description:
Circa two months ago I made a WAY LESS OFFENSIVE video on closely related themes, and (remarkably) it is only 8 minutes long, so I'd encourage you to also click through to: "For the Future of the Cause: Why Would Anyone "Do" Youtube?"
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ugYWMvDRmvs

Let's keep it real: most of you have no idea what I'm talking about when I say, "The Four Tops": https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=the+four+tops
